The '''Great Zelosi Sea''' was a large [[Ocean/Legends|ocean]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Zelos II]]. It contained [[Zelosian's Chine]], a massive [[Coral/Legends|coral]] outcropping that jutted from its surface. The ocean was inhabited by large numbers of [[melk]], a [[Reptile/Legends|reptilian]] scavenger.

